further customization, power-users can edit these files:</p><ul>
<li>conf.yml</li>
<li>pref.yml</li>
<li>patternlab-config.json</li>
</ul><p>Edit <code>conf.yml</code> to suit the needs of your development environment. If using Git,
<code>conf.yml</code> will not be version controlled by default.</p><p>Edit <code>pref.yml</code> to customize Fepper preferences. If you wish to use the
<code>fp syncback</code>, <code>fp frontend-copy</code>, or <code>fp template</code> tasks, you must supply
